Soft Skills\" con nuestro Simulador de Realidad Virtual! Ideal para profesionales que buscan mejorar sus habilidades interpersonales de forma inmersiva, interactiva y efectiva."}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "Softskills_Cover-Landscape-Padding.png", "id": "3682144288704654", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/57570314_3682144292037987_5131369632409068623_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=agk0O49utkIQ7kNvgETUjtc&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBIywHfs5faP-ANOw-lO1WoRb_YhCa09FLz3x_qOctVxg&oe=66E9597A"}, {"file_name": "SoftSkills_Logo_8100x1296px.png", "id": "1994020534333698", "image_type": "APP_IMG_LOGO_TRANSPARENT", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974910_1994020537667031_8688105079957652849_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=io63W8AzwLcQ7kNvgGQWkU7&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBZUnPQtjHUTI6EiS-J80GA46hSsPejqXcg3Ury_49lBQ&oe=66E97943"}, {"file_name": "SoftSkills_Cover-square_1440x1440px.png", "id": "1247184912914732", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_SQUARE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39035311_1247184916248065_2567077078745571082_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=vSgX89C-8lsQ7kNvgGBEA83&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDe5MVEyv-qekHYjfxsl0eLQWXs5Vp6ASN28RXJx2PfIg&oe=66E94F33"}, {"file_name": "INVELON_Icon-512x512px.png", "id": "1187254515612530", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974888_1187254518945863_7395065576696775988_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=YEMQNapybdYQ7kNvgHhHQVY&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYA5cmQLctjBO0xN1urKQWlBAirlP2t-ehw91AeBiR3KqA&oe=66E977C0"}, {"file_name": "SoftSkills_Cover-portrait_1008x1440px.png", "id": "1151595012723300", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982662_1151595016056633_8079137566055371486_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid